Qt is free for open source projects can be used for Linux/Android/Windows developent 
but requires registraion and license aggreement to use the online installer. 
Qt is used for GUI on all operatiing system and is required to build the GUI of No Limit Connect
Qt is available at https://www.qt.io/download (The open source use version may be hard to locate)

Visual Studio 2022 Community Edition can be used for No Limit Connect windows developement
and is free but requires registraion and license aggreement.  


All other tools used to build No Limit Connect DO NOT require registraion.



